    "rich_text_CQwnLV": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_n4gY8q": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/gas-cooktops-stove\">Gas Cooktops</a></h3><p>Gas cooktops are valued by Australian home cooks for their instant and precise heat control, making them ideal for everything from high-heat searing to gentle simmering. Whether you're preparing quick midweek dinners or hosting a weekend gathering, gas cooktops provide the flexibility to manage multiple dishes simultaneously. Our range includes models with wok burners and multiple cooking zones, offering flexibility for family meals and entertaining.</p><p>Choose from trusted brands such as <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/smeg-cooktops\">Smeg</a>, known for their Italian craftsmanship, <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/westinghouse/Cooktops\">Westinghouse</a> for practical, family-friendly designs, and <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/electrolux-cooktops\">Electrolux</a>, delivering modern, easy-to-use gas cooktops that blend seamlessly into your kitchen aesthetic.</p><p>Gas cooktops are easy to use and durable, with many models featuring flame failure safety devices for added peace of mind. With a focus on energy efficiency and performance, a gas cooktop from Cook & Bathe will become a trusted part of your daily cooking routine.</p><h3><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/induction\">Induction Cooktops</a></h3><p>Induction cooktops are the choice for homeowners seeking speed, precision, and energy efficiency in their kitchens. Using electromagnetic technology, induction cooktops heat your cookware directly while the surface remains cool, making them safe for families and easy to clean. Induction cooking is perfect for households looking to reduce energy consumption without compromising on performance.</p><p>At Cook & Bathe, we offer induction cooktops from leading brands such as <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/bora\">Bora</a>, known for their advanced downdraft extraction and sleek design, <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/franke-cooktops\">Franke</a> for their premium European styling, and <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/kleenmaid-cooktops\">Kleenmaid</a> for their balance of reliability and contemporary features.</p><p>Induction cooktops allow for rapid boiling, precise simmering, and a high level of control, helping you cook everything from sauces to stir-fries with ease. Many models include touch controls and flexible cooking zones, adding versatility and convenience to your kitchen.</p><h3><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/ceramic-cooktops\">Ceramic Cooktops</a></h3><p>Ceramic cooktops provide a sleek, modern look that enhances any kitchen while delivering consistent heat and straightforward functionality. The smooth glass surface makes cleaning up spills simple, while clearly marked cooking zones ensure ease of use during busy meal preparation.</p><p>Our selection includes ceramic cooktops from reputable brands such as <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/euro-appliances-cooktops\">Euro Appliances</a>, offering functional, stylish designs, and <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/smeg-cooktops\">Smeg</a>, bringing Italian design and advanced features to your kitchen. Ceramic cooktops are ideal for homeowners seeking a balance of performance, design, and practicality without the complexities of gas or induction cooking.</p><p>Whether you need a cooktop for a family kitchen, a compact apartment, or a stylish renovation project, ceramic cooktops are a reliable choice that complements your kitchen while making daily cooking simple and efficient.</p><p>At Cook & Bathe, we are dedicated to helping you find the perfect cooktop that aligns with your kitchen’s design and your cooking lifestyle. Explore our <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/cooktops\">full cooktops collection</a> or visit our showroom to receive expert advice and discover a cooktop that will enhance your kitchen for years to come.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
